{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 To install these scripts, import my repository into your Reapack :\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DaveInDev/Binbinhfr-Scripts/master/index.xml\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Available scripts :\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab bbh_lyricator : import and display smootly scrollable lyrics in a dedicated window\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab bbh_clean_sustain_cc : clean selected items of useless sustain pedal CC64 (between 1 and 126)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab bbh_midi_items_transpose : transpose selected items by a number of semitones\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab bbh_zoomwheel : adaptative Horizontal Zoom with Mousewheel\sa180\par}
